sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?x WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/deathCause> ?x . } ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri)) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

sparql2nl.en: What is the most common cause of death according to the DBpedia database?
sparql2nl.original_en: What is the most frequent cause of death?
sparql2nl.prompt:
